When Liam pays a madam for a specific fantasy to be made real, he assumes he’ll go home after three days with no harm done. His new captors have different plans, and with only a week left to live, escape seems impossible.Until Prince Briar walks in. Rumors say the pretty white hair and black wings hide a cruel streak. Despite his Prince of Pain nickname, he’ll surely let Liam go, right?Maybe, but only if Liam agrees to a deal that might have him jumping from the frypan and into the fire.